name: LOST IN SPACE
description: I had so much fun with that last one that I began to think of other phrases that could be just as meta in their meanings. What resulted was this: LOST IN SPACE. If we make a field of space using the actual word SPACE and then placed the word LOST within the words of SPACE in that field of SPACE, we've successfully create a visual meta phrase. It defines itself, which defines itself, which...you get the idea. It's so much fun to challenge the mind like this.
